item.title: 数据库索引[一]
item.description: This video really dives deep and explains the concept clearly: 1. Start from BST(Binary Search Tree) Consider how to solve LeetCode 704: Binary Search: Input: nums = [-1,0,3,5,9,12], target = 9 Output: 4 Explanation: 9 exists in nums and its index is 4 We use divide and conquer strategy and that reduces the time complexity of finding an element to O(logn) compared with O(n) of simple loop through the array from the very first element.
